v2.2.0
Added support for module loaders.
v2.1.0
Added 'buttonTag' option to allow changing of HTML tag used.
v2.0.0
Added to Bower.
Button classes for when SELECT is required or not.
License switched to MIT.
v1.2
Disabled buttons if select is disabled on load. Remember to update CSS file also.
Removed border from focused select box: especially prevalent on OSX
v1.1
Now keyboard accessible; break-out buttons are now <button> instead of <span> for native browser
keyboard selection. Also listens for focus on the select box, and sets it to opacity=1 when focused.
v1.0
Initial release
